      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" },
            "spanNulls": false,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "ops",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "max"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "title": "告警规则引用",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "options": {
        "content": "## 告警规则\n\n本仪表盘配合 `monitoring/circuit_breaker_alerts.yml` 使用，包含 8 条告警规则：\n\n| 告警 | 严重级别 | 触发条件 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| CircuitBreakerGlobalTriggered | critical | GLOBAL 级熔断触发 |\n| CircuitBreakerFrequentTrigger | warning | 5min 内触发 > 3 次 |\n| CircuitBreakerStuckOpen | warning | OPEN 状态 > 10min |\n| CircuitBreakerRecoveryLoop | warning | HALF_OPEN→OPEN 循环 > 3 次 |\n| CircuitBreakerUserLevelTriggered | warning | USER 级熔断触发 |\n| DegradeFrequentTrigger | warning | 5min 内降级 > 5 次 |\n| RateLimitFrequentTrigger | warning | 5min 内限流 > 10 次 |\n| CircuitBreakerMetricsMissing | warning | 指标缺失 5min |\n\n**文档**: [部署检查清单](file:///docs/DEPLOYMENT_CHECKLIST_circuit_breaker.md) | [技术文档](file:///docs/circuit_breaker_and_log_redaction.md) | [发布说明](file:///docs/RELEASE_NOTES_circuit_breaker.md)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    }
  ],
